### Search events by keyword (matches "Cloud Summit 2026" + "cloud-native" in its description)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events?$search=cloud
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Search events — combined with $filter
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events?$search=SAP&$filter=status eq 'published'
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Search events — combined with $orderby
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events?$search=development&$orderby=startDate desc
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Search sessions (matches "HANA Cloud Workshop")
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Events(ID=3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6,IsActiveEntity=true)/sessions?$search=workshop
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Search speakers by name
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Speakers?$search=Smith
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Search speakers by expertise (matches bio field — "enterprise integration")
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Speakers?$search=enterprise
Authorization: Basic admin:admin

### Search via RegistrationService (same annotation, different service)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/registration/Events?$search=cloud
Authorization: Basic attendee:attendee